<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Abhi's Flower Fusion</title>
    <style>
        
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

header {
    background: #0e0e0e;
    padding: 1em 0;
    text-align: center;
}

nav ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
}

nav ul li {
    display: inline;
    margin: 0 1em;
}

nav ul li a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
}

section {
    padding: 4em 2em;
    text-align: center;
}

#home {
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(67, 104, 214, 0.5), rgba(55, 163, 235, 0.5));
    color: rgb(7, 7, 7);
}

#about, #products, #contact, #customize {
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(67, 104, 214, 0.5), rgba(55, 163, 235, 0.5));
    margin-top: 1em;
}

.product {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 30%;
    margin: 1em;
}

.product img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
}

form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
}

form label {
    margin: 0.5em 0;
}

form input, form textarea, form button {
    width: 80%;
    padding: 0.5em;
    margin: 0.5em 0;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 4px;
}

form button {
    background: #0b0b0b;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
}

form button:hover {
    background: #1613f0;
    color: rgb(253, 250, 250);

}

footer {
    background: #333;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.3em 0;
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
}
 
    </style>
   <script>
    function showAlert() {
        alert("Thanks for contacting us!");
        document.getElementById("contactForm").reset(); // Reset the form fields
        return false; // Prevents the form from submitting
    }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="#products">Products</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="home">
        <h1>Welcome to Abhi's Flower Fusion</h1>
        <p>Discover our beautiful collection of flowers.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Abhi's Flower Fusion, where every bloom tells a story. Founded in 2020, our shop is dedicated to providing exquisite floral arrangements for all occasions. 
            We proudly source the freshest flowers from local growers to ensure the highest quality. 
            Our skilled team of florists combines creativity and expertise to craft stunning designs that make every event memorable. 
            Whether you're planning a wedding, celebrating a special moment, or simply brightening someone's day, we offer custom arrangements and prompt delivery. 
            Discover the beauty of flowers with us in online or at <br><b>Flora Avenue at floor no 12,Tolli choke line no 9,Navi Mumbai 0890001. <br/></b> Thank you for choosing Abhi's Flower Fusion 
            â€”we're excited to bring a touch of floral magic into your life!
        </p>
    </section>

    <section id="products">
        <h2>Our Products</h2>
        <div class="product">
            <img src="/images/redrose.jpg" alt="Red Rose" style="width: 200px; height: 300px;">
            <h3>Red Rose</h3>
            <p>A rose is a timeless symbol of love and beauty, enchanting hearts w
                ith its delicate petals and captivating fragrance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product">
            <img src="images/blueorchidflowers.jpg" alt="blueorchidflowers" style="width: 200px; height: 300px;">
            <h3>Blue Orchides</h3>
            <p>Exotic flowers known for their vibrant blue color and unique petal shapes, symbolizing rarity and beauty.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product">
            <img src="images/lilies.jpg" alt="lilies" style="width: 200px; height: 300px;">
            <h3>Lilies</h3>
            <p>Elegant flowers known for their large, fragrant blooms and wide variety of colors.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="product">
            <img src="images/sunflower.jpg" alt="sunflowe" style="width: 200px; height: 300px;">
            <h3>Sunflower</h3>
            <p>Tall, bright flowers that follow the sun, symbolizing loyalty and adoration.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="product">
            <img src="images/tulips.png" alt="Tulip"  style="width: 200px; height: 300px;">
            <h3>Tulip</h3>
            <p>Elegant and simple flowers available in many colors, representing perfect love and springtime renewal.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="customize">
        <h1>To customize</h1>
        <p>Reach our store at Navi Mumbai <br> or <br> Choose customize option in the <a href="/dashboard">dashboard</a>
            </p>
            <section id="contact">
                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                <form action="#" onsubmit="return showAlert()">
                    <label for="name">Name:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                    
                    <label for="email">Email:</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                    
                    <label for="message">Message:</label>
                    <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
                    
                    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
                </form>
            </section>
            
            
            

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Flower Shop. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    
</body>
</html>
